em in light of the recent developments.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aIslamxRelationsxJudaism. 0aJews in the Hadith. 0aJews in the Qurʼan. 0aJudaismxRelationsxIslam. 7aRELIGION / Islam / Koran & Sacred Writings.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Backlist eBook-Package 2008-2015z978311068814608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2014z97831110237000 cprintz978161811379540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161811380140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781618113801423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781618113801/original  a978-3-11-068814-6  Academic Studies Press Backlist eBook-Package 2008-2015c2008d2015  a978-3-11-102370-0  Academic Studies Press Complete eBook-Package 2014b2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK